<i>The brazen attack happened</i>

40:29.940 --> 40:32.350
<i>in the middle of the day</i>
<i>at a political rally.</i>

40:32.550 --> 40:35.050
<i>Senator Evers was airlifted</i>
<i>to the hospital,</i>

40:35.240 --> 40:37.400
<i>but has since passed away.</i>

40:37.600 --> 40:40.010
<i>This afternoon, the shooting</i>
<i>death of Senator Evers</i>

40:40.210 --> 40:42.100
<i>- on the campaign trail</i>
- [phone chimes]

40:42.300 --> 40:44.580
<i>along with her security agent</i>
